Installation

Here are the sequence of commands used to get the app up and running.

    $ git clone git://github.com/perlpilot/ttt.git
    $ cd ttt
    $ cpanm --installdeps .         # make sure we get all of the dependencies
    $ cpanm --test-only .           # run the tests
    $ plackup bin/app.psgi          # run the app

